The '''Galactic Institute of Anthropology''' was an institution that at some point published the works ''[[Mandalorians: Identity and Its Influence on Genome]]'' and ''[[Mandalorians: Identity and Language]]''.<ref name="Insider86" />

==Behind the scenes==
The Galactic Institute of Anthropology was first mentioned in the article "[[The Mandalorians: People and Culture]]," written by [[Karen Traviss]] and published in the [[Star Wars Insider 86|eighty-sixth issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine<ref name="Insider86" /> that was released on [[February 13]], [[2006]].<ref name="SW.com">{{SWArchive|url=community/fanclub/mag/news20060125.html|text=Inside ''Star Wars Insider'' #86}}</ref>

